block content
	h1 Scavenger Hunt
	h2 Grab your phone and grab some friends and connect to our game to compete in a photo scavenger hunt! Start by selecting one of our premade hunts below, or create your own!  
	script
		function show(id) {
			document.getElementById(id).style.visibility = "visible";
		}
		function hide(id) {
			document.getElementById(id).style.visibility = "hidden";
		}
	script

